- don't include figs in pdf
- don't remove packages from latex header
- for initial submission upload pdf inc. fig legend but w/o embedded figs
- refs should be in .tex file, not in separate .bib
- no \input or \include commands
- follow instructions in template for fig legends and cits
- Elements that exceed the width of the text column must be included in an “adjustwidth” environment to display properly. See the template for more information.
- figs should be as .tiff or .eps

- no length requirement for manuscripts
- double spaced
- up to 3 heading levels

- asked to suggest suitable editors and *at least 4* potential reviewers (bearing in mind poss. competing interests)
